{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/vmxk3u18","slide":1,"name":"text","text":"PROTECT BEFORE TRUST BECOMES A TRANSFER.","textPreview":"PROTECT BEFORE TRUST BECOMES A TRANSFER.","textChars":40,"textLines":1,"bbox":[62,482,510,52]}
{"kind":"image","id":"im/z25srupc","slide":1,"name":"","alt":"Vietnamese customer reading a suspicious identity verification message at night","bbox":[0,0,1280,720]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/u23s8c","slide":1,"text":"Imagine receiving a Zalo message from someone claiming to be VNeID support. The logo looks correct. They know your name. They tell you to verify immediately, install an app, or scan a QR code.\nYou have maybe two minutes to decide whether to trust it.\nThis is the moment CheckVar 2.0 is built for: protecting customers before trust becomes a transfer."}
