{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/by98rips","slide":3,"name":"text","text":"An answer while the customer can still stop.","textPreview":"An answer while the customer can still stop.","textChars":44,"textLines":1,"bbox":[62,554,400,62]}
{"kind":"image","id":"im/ux87u1cb","slide":3,"name":"","alt":"Premium smartphone combining screenshot link QR and recipient evidence into one scan","bbox":[0,0,1280,720]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/3wvfyt","slide":3,"text":"CheckVar gives customers one simple place to check evidence.\nThey can paste a message, enter a link or recipient, upload a screenshot, or scan a QR code.\nWe analyse the evidence together—not as isolated pieces—and return an answer while the customer can still stop the transaction."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/g7c42h","slide":4,"title":"CHECKVAR 2.0","textShapes":10}
