{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/dwjelsf2","slide":4,"name":"text","text":"STOP  ·  CALL THE BANK  ·  REPORT","textPreview":"STOP  ·  CALL THE BANK  ·  REPORT","textChars":33,"textLines":1,"bbox":[62,552,460,28]}
{"kind":"image","id":"im/21w3mhor","slide":4,"name":"","alt":"Three evidence artifacts locking into one fraud campaign fingerprint","bbox":[0,0,1280,720]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/g7c42h","slide":4,"text":"We don’t simply show a red warning.\nCheckVar explains why: this phrase appeared in previous reports; this domain distributes a suspicious APK; this beneficiary is connected to confirmed cases.\nThe customer receives clear actions: stop the transfer, contact the bank, and optionally report the case anonymously.\nThat explanation is essential for trust."}
