{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/a5ob29gv","slide":5,"name":"text","text":"Every connection stays reviewable.","textPreview":"Every connection stays reviewable.","textChars":34,"textLines":1,"bbox":[62,532,360,30]}
{"kind":"image","id":"im/ru9cr6pg","slide":5,"name":"","alt":"Anonymous report becoming durable fraud signals and joining a campaign intelligence loop","bbox":[0,0,1280,720]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/vqslbl","slide":5,"text":"The anonymous report does not disappear into a support inbox.\nCheckVar extracts durable signals—accounts, phone numbers, domains and QR payloads—and connects them to existing campaigns.\nThe matching is intentionally conservative. We do not force every suspicious case into a campaign. Every connection remains reviewable by an analyst."}
