{"kind":"image","id":"im/gnmlk7yt","slide":7,"name":"","alt":"Vietnamese bank customer safely completing a transfer while intelligence protects the next customer","bbox":[0,0,1280,720]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/u6yh81","slide":7,"text":"Vietnam does not need another static scam-warning page. Customers need help at the exact moment they are making a decision, and banks need the intelligence to act on the campaign behind it.\nCheckVar 2.0 connects those two moments.\nOur next step is a focused 30-day pilot with one bank and one high-volume scam type. We will measure one outcome: how much we reduce the time from the first signal to customer protection.\nCheck the evidence. Connect the campaign. Protect every transfer.\nKey line: Scammers change identities faster than banks can publish warnings. CheckVar turns every customer check into an opportunity to stop the campaign."}